<p>黑板报篇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200918/66d55cd4f45c4c1f8ce5b3efe95105bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200918/eefa8a6b4fac47feab2c62b9c438d5e5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>通过黑板报、橱窗大力宣传“厉行节约，杜绝浪费”理念，树立正确的价值观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200918/e1ba3d99bcba4e5598b43285805cc9d2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
